_aChangeLog.text: Added more than 13 spawns, issue with server plugins that usually runs sm_ublock and allows multi-use of spawn points
Added signs to each game to help people learn the map quicker
Lowered chance of hard drive spawn
Fixed players still having up to 250hp when exiting hunger games (reset hp to 100 on exit)
Fixed any displacements which were a power of 4 (crash/clipping issues)
Fixed a corrupted nav file (no more nav :})
Fixed Hound secret killing you when you looked up (I think idk)
Moved Green Herb from the truck because it kept getting stolen :/
Fixed a bug with a brush clipping thru the wall in surf
Increased ammo capacity in hunger games
Fixed issue with the win trigger on surf being hit when you don't make it
Added TP to low grav game because the ladder was fucking wit my gravity shit
Fixed weird shadow lighting on the wooden platforms in Main Cell area
Added Jin player model to first CT to select the AWP :]
Packed a null/dummy nav file to prevent the corrupted one from being used by anyone who had the previous version of f7
Added custom soundscape files to prevent the dsp being set back to 0, as even using server or client command to set it is undone on soundscape change
Made the lava, actually like, lava (fullbright texture)

_sText:
jb_resi, a Jailbreak map for CS:Source themed around the Resident Evil franchise.
there are many secrets... many many many more than you will ever find :}

Games:


  • Drop Down / 4 Corners [50/50]
  • Surf
  • Boss Fight
  • Low Grav Bhop / Low Grav Climb [50/50]
  • Colours (s1, s2 & s3)
  • Deathrun (9 traps)
  • Trail Blazing (s1 & s2)
  • Death Crate
  • Extreme Climb
  • HNS
  • Trikz (1 - 7 custom kz tricks)
  • Hunger Games (TP from box in cell area near surf)
  • Dodge Course (s1 & s2)
  • Ladder KZ (easy / hard [50/50])
  • Box Climb (easy/ hard [50/50])
  • Man Cannon
  • Random Climb (1-5 random climbs spawn over the pond)
  • Bomb Toss
  • LJ Blocks
  • Lava Climb (1-3 random climbs over lava (near dodgecourse))
